name: Ashley_Series_42-inch_Wood_Glass_Wall_Cabinet
description:
This on the wall cabinet is a great way to decorate or improve storage in a living space. With nearly 3.5-inches deep of space inside the cabinet, this cabin with its natural pine finish can be painted or stained to whatever color or style you want.
